1. Purpose

This document defines the mathematical backbone for VCF Geometry Engine v1.0, establishing a stable, reproducible framework for preprocessing, normalizing, vectorizing, and interpreting macro-financial data using geometric methods.
This is the foundational spec for Claude, GitHub Copilot, and all future code contributors.

